---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Practice — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Learn about the story, mission, team, and values behind Oasis Dental Care in Huntington Beach. Led by Dr. Jason Fu with over 25 years of experience."
  page="about"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="tag">/ Our Practice</span>
    <h1>The Oasis Dental Story</h1>
    <p>A warm, personal approach supported by modern techniques, clear communication, and a team that genuinely cares about the community we serve.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book an appointment <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission -->
<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="practice-split reveal">
      <div class="practice-copy">
        <span class="tag">Our Mission</span>
        <h2>Care grounded in trust, precision, and respect.</h2>
        <p>For many years, Oasis Dental Care has served the Huntington Beach community with a warm, personal approach supported by modern techniques and clear communication.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px">Our goal is to provide dependable dental care grounded in professionalism, clarity, and respect for your comfort. We combine experience with up-to-date diagnostic tools such as digital imaging and detailed examinations, helping you make confident, informed decisions about your treatment.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:16px">Every visit is designed to support long-term oral health through early detection, preventive education, and solutions tailored to your individual needs.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:28px"><a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule a visit</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="practice-media">
        <div class="ph-block">
          <div class="ph-inner">
            <div class="ph-ic">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ph-title">Office photo</div>
            <div class="ph-sub">Placeholder — add your practice interior or team photo here.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ph-badge">
            <span class="pulse" style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal-300)"></span>
            Huntington Beach, CA
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Stat band -->
<div class="stat-band reveal">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stat-row">
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">25+</div><div class="l">Years of experience</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">10k+</div><div class="l">Smiles cared for</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">5.0★</div><div class="l">Patient rated</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="n">Same-day</div><div class="l">Emergency care</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Our Dental Team -->
<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div><span class="tag">Our Dental Team</span><h2>Familiar faces, every visit.</h2></div>
    </div>
    <p class="team-intro reveal">Our staff, including hygienists, assistants, and front office team members, works together to create a smooth, comfortable experience at every visit. Many patients see the same team members visit after visit, creating a sense of familiarity and continuity that helps reduce anxiety and build long-term trust.</p>

    <div class="team reveal" style="margin-top:42px">

      <!-- Dr. Fu -->
      <div class="member">
        <div class="photo">
          <img src="https://oasisdentalcarehb.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dr-Jason-Fu-2021.jpg" alt="Dr. Jason Fu" />
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <div class="nm">Dr. Jason Fu</div>
          <div class="rl">Lead Dentist &amp; Founder</div>
          <p>Dr. Fu brings over 25 years of clinical experience, combining advanced dental expertise with a calm, patient-focused approach. He is committed to delivering thoughtful, individualized care for every patient who walks through the door.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Leandre -->
      <div class="member">
        <div class="photo">
          <div class="ph">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            <span>Photo after photoshoot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <div class="nm">Leandre</div>
          <div class="rl">Lead Back Office Manager</div>
          <p>Leandre plays an essential role in the clinical flow of each day. From preparing treatment rooms to coordinating care alongside Dr. Fu, he helps ensure that appointments run efficiently and comfortably.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Edith -->
      <div class="member">
        <div class="photo">
          <div class="ph">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            <span>Photo after photoshoot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
          <div class="nm">Edith</div>
          <div class="rl">Office Manager</div>
          <p>Edith is frequently the first point of contact for many patients. She welcomes you at the front desk, assists with scheduling, and provides thoughtful guidance on insurance coverage, financial arrangements, and preparing for your visit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="team-note reveal">We believe that excellent dentistry is not only about clinical skill—it's about relationships, consistency, and the comfort that comes from being known and cared for by a team who genuinely values your well-being.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Values -->
<section class="pad tech" id="values">
  <div class="bg-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <div><span class="tag">Our Core Values</span><h2>What guides everything we do.</h2></div>
      <p>Five principles that shape every patient interaction from the moment you walk in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid reveal">

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Clear Communication</h3>
        <p>We explain findings from exams, digital x-rays, and treatment recommendations in straightforward language, ensuring you understand your options.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Consistency</h3>
        <p>You'll see the same doctor and a stable staff, rather than rotating providers. Familiarity breeds trust and helps us better understand your needs over time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Comfort and Care</h3>
        <p>Our approach prioritizes gentle techniques, patient pacing, and a welcoming environment so every visit feels as stress-free as possible.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Prevention Focus</h3>
        <p>Routine cleanings, hygiene guidance, exams, and digital imaging help catch small issues early and prevent more extensive treatment later.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vcard">
        <div class="v-ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Community-Oriented</h3>
        <p>We are proud to care for families, individuals, and local residents throughout Huntington Beach—a community we're honored to call home.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ctacard reveal">
      <div class="grid-ov"></div>
      <div class="c">
        <span class="tag">New patients welcome</span>
        <h2>Come experience the difference.</h2>
        <p>We'd love to welcome you to Oasis Dental Care. Book a visit and see what patient-centered dentistry really looks like.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acts">
        <a class="btn" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
        <a class="btn btn-o" href="/contact">Request appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
/* practice page layout */
.practice-split {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: center;
}
@media(max-width: 880px) {
  .practice-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
}
.practice-copy h2 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 44px);
  margin-top: 14px;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}
.practice-copy p {
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  font-size: 16.5px;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.practice-media {
  position: relative;
}
.ph-block {
  aspect-ratio: 4/4.5;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,129,116,.04) 0 14px, transparent 14px 28px), var(--dark-2);
  border-radius: 18px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.ph-inner {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 24px;
  border: 1.5px dashed rgba(95,208,192,.32);
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 24px;
}
.ph-ic {
  width: 58px;
  height: 58px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(95,208,192,.4);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
}
.ph-ic svg {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.5;
}
.ph-title {
  font-family: var(--disp);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #eaf6f3;
}
.ph-sub {
  font-size: 13.5px;
  color: #86b3ab;
  max-width: 230px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.ph-badge {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 18px;
  right: 18px;
  background: rgba(8,34,31,.82);
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 9px 12px;
  font-size: 11.5px;
  letter-spacing: .01em;
  color: var(--teal-300);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

/* stat band */
.stat-band {
  background: var(--dark);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 40px 0;
}
.stat-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 0;
}
.stat {
  padding: 0 32px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
  text-align: center;
}
.stat:last-child { border-right: 0; }
.stat .n {
  font-family: var(--disp);
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--teal-300);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.stat .l {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #7fb3ab;
  margin-top: 6px;
  letter-spacing: .01em;
}
@media(max-width: 680px) {
  .stat-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .stat { padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .stat:nth-child(even) { border-right: 0; }
}

/* team extras */
.team-intro {
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  font-size: 17px;
  max-width: 720px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.team-note {
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  font-size: 16px;
  max-width: 680px;
  margin-top: 36px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  padding: 24px 28px;
  border: 1px solid var(--line-l);
  border-radius: 14px;
  background: var(--panel);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* values grid */
.values-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 14px;
  margin-top: 42px;
}
@media(max-width: 900px) { .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media(max-width: 560px) { .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.vcard {
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 28px;
  background: var(--dark-2);
}
.v-ic {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 11px;
  background: rgba(95,208,192,.12);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.v-ic svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  stroke: var(--teal-300);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 1.7;
}
.vcard h3 {
  font-size: 19px;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.vcard p {
  color: #a9ccc5;
  font-size: 14.5px;
  line-height: 1.65;
}
</style>
